annotationA: DEAD box protein 21E2 (Dbp21E2) is an essential protein and a member of a family of DEAD box RNA helicases. Photoreceptors lacking Dbp21E2 function show defects in rhodopsin biogenesis and the maintenance of photoreceptors, leading to cell degeneration
annotationB: LD11580p; mRNA binding; ATP binding; ATP-dependent RNA helicase activity
